{"tid":1630382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有班仆街帶風向要停止勇武行動","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:21:12.000Z","uid":50987,"like":28,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4bea7db02cfe6c17885d3f26d9ab23e89d837563","tid":1630382,"uid":50987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母用撚左緊急法都咁少反應既話咪姐係叫港共變本加厲<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候仲計較班垃圾左膠做乜撚<br />\n<br />\n現實d得唔得，今時今日仲有無可能做到和平示威啊<br />\n<br />\n我地示威唔係玩馬戲團啊，外國人想睇和平遊行唔係大撚曬架<br />\n<br />\n搶返主動權得唔得？唔需要跟垃圾政府個劇本黎行架"},{"pid":"6df7c72688929abcbecc56514e934d22ab21b1d2","tid":1630382,"uid":303304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09c34af07e92d0b0da07f6fdc9ef79719545fe03","tid":1630382,"uid":73200,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dcdd7e80dc7817df2af6c51bcdd780b24418f12","tid":1630382,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c01c40eaba724fb2a277db3eae308714d6cb4619","tid":1630382,"uid":38691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:04.000Z","msg":"搞清楚啦 唔係停止呀 係暫停呀 畀機會美國過法案呀"},{"pid":"00fcf712c37ddd12b52389aa54ad10b281e80550","tid":1630382,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"81f1a112a20de35ce5baafd7f7cef2c7c49c6e5b","tid":1630382,"uid":50987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"救下你地繼續玩快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要無俾狗咬就已經係成功"},{"pid":"83178e05006cbad2b879624fc5928f73d6bc3cab","tid":1630382,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ad7bcd499789fe6e1cdd402fc1013844a18917","tid":1630382,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"和平示威係港島 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bb83b1fc27c1e7a714082cfa2821a29ead5937","tid":1630382,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"左膠等咗好耐喇"},{"pid":"caa89c169602838374ebfde72bd5990a8fa0e72f","tid":1630382,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:01.000Z",